    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, reflecting a standard of preservation that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail adheres to an uncompromising level of excellence. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition, which represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
