      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! It is in absolute showroom condition\u2014seriously, you won\u2019t find a single blemish. It drives like a dream and has been loved and pampered every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for a car that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come by and see it for yourself!",
